{"tid":611967,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"躁男擸刀大鬧旺角馬會 被捕後解釋：把刀用嚟切生果","createTime":"2018-03-31T13:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T14:00:18.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b8bd24d972455841e743cbfe9d309e9977ead9","tid":611967,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T13:59:18.000Z","msg":"傍晚6時許，一名男子在旺角花園街的馬會投注站內，疑因提款問題與職員爭執，大吵大鬧，其間更一度亮刀指嚇對方，職員見狀大驚報警。警員接報趕至，將男子㩒地制服，他涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器被捕，帶返警署扣查。<br />\n<br />\n讀者鍾先生向《蘋果》表示，事發一刻他正在馬會內，突然見到有一名身穿黑色衫、身型健碩的男子，在門外被兩名警員按在地上，不停掙扎反抗。鍾憶述當時馬會職員向在場的警員表示，疑犯要求拎錢才亮刀，惟他不停高呼：「我邊有犯法，你做乜捉我」。大約數分鐘後，多名警員趕至現場增援，疑犯被3名警員合力抬上警車。<br />\n據鍾生提供的片段中所見，現場有一名警長一邊收拾疑犯散落地上的物品時，一邊向疑犯表示：「你都幾巴閉，打劫馬會呀，聽日你就名垂千古呀」，而鍾形容當時疑犯神志清醒，不斷坐在警車向警員解釋：「我把刀用嚟切生果咋嘛」。<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/2/23/Occupycentral_tvb_knief.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/699?cb=20141005040135\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F2%2F23%2FOccupycentral_tvb_knief.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F699%3Fcb%3D20141005040135&h=36be254b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180331/58019415\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180331%2F58019415&d=zOqsE2T5ru%2FC5poOCLdd7MmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=4c2c6cb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180331%2F58019415&h=95f1e4a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180331/58019415</a>"},{"pid":"c2af9edc0bb32c7a7d7079654c80bb5969decf57","tid":611967,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}